From efc78f81b5c35c18faa4a8ffb686d698aae50eb5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Gregory Williams <gregory.williams@amd.com>
Date: Tue, 24 Mar 2026 13:27:41 -0700
Subject: [AIENGINE PATCH V2 1/2] driver: src: global: Add support for more aie2ps
 perf counters

In aie2ps there is now 6 counters in shim tile and 4 counters in core
tile memory module. This patch adds members to support the higher number
of counters. For these new counters, there is an initial offset 0x8
between CtrlReg0 and CtrlReg1. There is also now more than 1 reset
control register and only 2 perf counters are controlled per register
instead of the usual 4.

Signed-off-by: Gregory Williams <gregory.williams@amd.com>
---
